        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2481056306" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17964714909078268501">There&apos;s something enchanting in the way Calvino writes. Far from matching the dazzling beauty of Invisible Cities, The Nonexistent Knight remains nothing short of a delightful read. Calvino, as if impersonating Monty Python, signs this lovely parody of the Medieval Age.</span>
  <span id="freeText17964714909078268501" style="display:none">There's something enchanting in the way Calvino writes. Far from matching the dazzling beauty of Invisible Cities, The Nonexistent Knight remains nothing short of a delightful read. Calvino, as if impersonating Monty Python, signs this lovely parody of the Medieval Age.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17964714909078268501" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

